title: Bluemars (Music for the Space Traveller) - Cryosleep (Zero Beat
description:
This is a rip of the excellent but often unavailable streams from Bluemars.org . I spent more than a week ripping these streams to ensure that the entire collection was included. When ripping streams the song separation isn&#039;t always perfect (the ripping software has to make good guesses about where one song ends and another begins) but with most songs it&#039;s correct. If anyone wants to go for extra credit and create a torrent with the proper official mp3s at a higher bitrate, well that&#039;d be just awesome.


-Ripped with Streamripper
-Like the streams, all mp3s are 128k bitrate
-Some songs may be duplicated between Bluemars and Cryosleep, but that&#039;s the price of keeping it accurate.
-This was ripped after the recent update to the streams (he added new songs). Unfortunately I don&#039;t have a rip of the old songsets.
-This is my first torrent, please tell me what you think!
